NK010(tha)020:0: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs las zor las gnam lcags 'bar ba bzhugs /

NK010(tha)020:2306: brnag pa'i khong du dug mda' g.yos //
NK010(tha)020:2307: khro mo bcu yi phyag brnyan te //
NK010(tha)020:2308: mon mo 'di ltar ya mtshan can //
NK010(tha)020:2309: mon mo'i lus la phra men mgo //
NK010(tha)020:2310: g.yas pa rtags kyi phyag mtshan la //
NK010(tha)020:2311: g.yon pa zor gyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK010(tha)020:2312: phur bu'i zor 'phen khra la la //
NK010(tha)020:2313: nyung mo'i zor 'phen si li li //
NK010(tha)020:2314: mtshon zor mang po zings se zing //
NK010(tha)020:2315: dug zor mang po thibs se thib //
NK010(tha)020:2316: nad khrag khrag zor chi li li //
NK010(tha)020:2317: khrag zor chen po dgra la ya //
NK010(tha)020:2318: brnag pa'i khong du dug mda' g.yos //
NK010(tha)020:2320: shwa na las kyi mkha' 'gro ma //
NK010(tha)020:2321: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu dang //
NK010(tha)020:2322: gser gyi 'phar ba lce brgyad ma //
NK010(tha)020:2323: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum ma //
NK010(tha)020:2324: zas su sha za khrag 'thung ma //
NK010(tha)020:2325: g.yas su phur zor mda' ltar 'phen //
NK010(tha)020:2326: g.yon du khrag zor mtsho ltar rlog /
NK010(tha)020:2327: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK010(tha)020:2328: da ni 'phen pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)020:2329: khrag mda' khrag sbur chi li li //
NK010(tha)020:2330: khrag mda' bu yug char ltar phob //
NK010(tha)020:2331: dgra bo'i khong du dug mda' rgyob //
NK010(tha)020:2332: bdag nyid ma dang sa bdag ma //
NK010(tha)020:2333: las kyi mkha' 'gro rnam gsum yang //
NK010(tha)020:2334: khrag zor dmar po'i sna drongs la //
NK010(tha)020:2335: khrag zor me ltar mched nas kyang //
NK010(tha)020:2336: dam nyams dgra bo 'tshig par gyis //
NK010(tha)020:2337: khrag zor chu ltar 'brub nas kyang //
NK010(tha)020:2338: dam nyams dgra bo 'khyer bar gyis //
NK010(tha)020:2339: las kyis mnar ba'i byur ngan 'di //
NK010(tha)020:2340: drag po'i shugs kyis mi bsgral du //
NK010(tha)020:2342: snying khrag choms shig gu lu na //
NK010(tha)020:2343: rnam shes sdoms shig shwa na ram //
NK010(tha)020:2344: srog rtsa chod cig su tri ram //
NK010(tha)020:2345: phog par rgyob cig snying gi dkyil //
NK010(tha)020:2346: gnad du rgyob cig srog gi rtsa //
NK010(tha)020:2347: brnag pa'i khong du khrag zor g.yos //
NK010(tha)020:2348: khrag zor dmar po'i sna drongs shig /
NK010(tha)020:2349: zor 'phang tshur la ma log cig /
NK010(tha)020:2350: gnyen byas dgra ru ma ldang zhig /
NK010(tha)020:2351: zas sbyor dug tu ma g.yo zhig /
NK010(tha)020:2352: nyams pa gang yin yul mkhar sgyel //
NK010(tha)020:2353: mi nad me ltar mched nas kyang //
NK010(tha)020:2354: nyams pa gang yin phung bar gyis //
NK010(tha)020:2355: dmag sna drongs shing drag po zor gyi lha //
NK010(tha)020:2356: b+h+yo b+h+yo drag po zor gyi thun phob cig /
NK010(tha)020:2357: ces brjod la thod pa dang /
NK010(tha)020:2358: rwa zor du gnas pa'i khrag mdas sna drangs pa'i zor rdzas rnams rab dgra bo'i dur ma chad /
NK010(tha)020:2360: tha ma yul phyogs su 'phangs na rim pa bzhin du bdun brgyud dang /
NK010(tha)020:2362: dmigs bya kha phung du 'gro ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)020:2364: drag po las kyi sbyor ba ni //
NK010(tha)020:2365: mtshan ngan thod pa chen po ru //
NK010(tha)020:2366: khrag dang dug dang phye ma gsum //
NK010(tha)020:2367: bsgrub bya'i ling+gara ldan pa la //
NK010(tha)020:2368: sngags nas dpal gyi sku nyid kyis //
NK010(tha)020:2369: bstan pa 'jig par byed pa yi //
NK010(tha)020:2370: skye bo de la 'phang gyur na //
NK010(tha)020:2371: tshangs pa'i tshe dang ldan pa yang //
NK010(tha)020:2373: de bas 'di ni drag po'i las //
NK010(tha)020:2374: gsang chen nga yi bstan pa yin //
NK010(tha)020:2376: gsum pa las mjug bros bsdu ba ni /
NK010(tha)020:2377: sgrub khang gi sgo drung du dgra bgegs la 'gugs 'dren byas /
NK010(tha)020:2378: me chu'i steng du gtor gzhong ri rab tu bsam pa sbub la /
NK010(tha)020:2379: lag pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas las bzhi dang bstun pa'i bro ra bca' zhing /
NK010(tha)020:2381: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)020:2382: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad kun //
NK010(tha)020:2383: khro bor ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)020:2384: thams cad thal ba rdul du rlogs //
NK010(tha)020:2385: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)020:2389: dbang gi khro bor ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)020:2390: thams cad dbang du 'du bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)020:2391: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya wa shang ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)020:2393: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)020:2394: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad kun //
NK010(tha)020:2395: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)020:2396: tshe dang bsod nams rgyas par mdzod //
NK010(tha)020:2397: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya push+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)020:2399: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)020:2400: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad kun //
NK010(tha)020:2401: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)020:2402: thams cad ma lus zhi bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)020:2403: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)020:2405: rdo rje gzhon nu'i zhabs kyis mnan //
NK010(tha)020:2407: khro bo'i tshogs kyi zas su bsngo //
NK010(tha)020:2408: bskal pa'i me yi phung pos bsreg /
NK010(tha)020:2409: ye shes me yis bag chags bsreg /
NK010(tha)020:2410: nyon mongs lnga dang ldan pa yi //
NK010(tha)020:2411: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)020:2412: byang chub sems ni ma skyes bar //
NK010(tha)020:2413: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK010(tha)020:2416: g+h+ri h+n+aa pa ya g+h+ri h+n+aa pa ya h'u /
NK010(tha)020:2417: +aa na ya ho b+ha ga w+aa na bid+ya r+aa dza h'u phata /
NK010(tha)020:2419: bzhi pa phyogs skyong dang rgyal chen bzhi la gtang rag btang ba ni /
NK010(tha)020:2420: gtor gzhong sman phud dang 'brus bkang /
NK010(tha)020:2421: gser skyems dang gtor ma 'bul ba spyi ltar ro //
NK010(tha)020:2423: nang du log nas tshe yi snying po bzlas /
NK010(tha)020:2424: cho ga'i rjes chog rnams gzhung bzhin bya'o //
